Summary: Taking pictures of western sky and noticed this object. It was not a plane.
trends: There has been one other sighting in Good Hope
There were no other sightings in Good Hope on or around October 18th 2012
divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking pictures as I do almost everyday, hoping to catch a good sunset.I am on my property. I noticed the object immediately and noticed it didn't appear to be moving, as a plane would. I began taking pictures over a five minute period. The object appeared stationary. I have seen something that I can't explain. It vanished when I looked back up from petting the dog. In addition, i looked at the pictures with a contrast and a photo negative Photoscape action and was very surprised at what I saw. I'm not claiming its anything. The inclosed pictures are unretouched.
